<collectingRegion box="[275,340,1444,1469]" country="Brazil" name="Bahia" pageId="8" pageNumber="159">Bahia</collectingRegion>
State. This study extends its known distribution and represents the first record for the state of 
<collectingRegion box="[151,265,1479,1504]" country="Brazil" name="Maranhao" pageId="8" pageNumber="159">Maranhão</collectingRegion>
